This is a "Lock" demo for the feature FSM (Finite State Machine) of Akka.
Compatible with Akka 1.3.
See: http://cntt.tv/nodes/show/559

Checkout:

cd /tmp
git clone http://github.com/ngocdaothanh/lock-fsm-akka.git

Build and run with SBT 0.11.2:

cd /tmp/lock-fsm-akka
sbt console

From the SBT console:

import akka.actor.Actor
import demo.{Lock, Button}
val lock = Actor.actorOf(new Lock("2552"))
lock.start
lock ! Button('2')
lock ! Button('5')
lock ! Button('5')
lock ! Button('2')
lock.stop

To quit the SBT console:

import akka.actor.Actors
Actors.registry.shutdownAll()
Actors.remote.shutdown()
:q
